THE ROLE
Expand all
Boux Avenue - a stylish, innovative lingerie brand that is an irresistible shopping haven for lingerie, nightwear, swimwear and accessories - is looking for enthusiastic, fresh and confident people to be part of their team. If you are ready to take on this challenge, join us and boost your career.
Sales, Customer & Operations:
Lead team in achieving store targets;
Lead team in achieving store performance requirements;
Analyze and monitor sales/stocks;
Recommend ways to improve the brand and store performance;
Provide exceptional customer;
Ensure high customer satisfaction;
Ensure detailed knowledge of product and services;
Ensure smooth complaint resolution;
Assist all in-store marketing activities/events;
Standards:
Ensure strict compliance with brand procedures and policies in stock, sales and merchandising;
Ensure Health, Safety & Emergency procedures;
Effectively manage administrative work;
Ensure protection of company's assets;
Ensure impeccable execution of brand manager requests;
Training:
Motivate, train and develop team members to ensure store goals are achieved;
Guide team members by improving skills and capabilities on sales, conduct and operational procedures, product knowledge and interpersonal skills;
Reporting & Communication:
Communicate all customer/merchandise quality feedback to assist in the brand decision making process;
Ensure communication from Head Office to all team;
Ensure clear and relevant communication flow with brand manager.
REQUIREMENTS
Education:
High School graduate;
Sales and fashion focused;
Strong organizational skills;
Strong communication, leadership, interpersonal understanding;
Customer oriented, well-presented and a true team player;
Ability to comply and ensure strict quality standards;
Relevant Experience:
At least 4 years experience as Store Manager or Assistant Store Manager in fashion retail industry in a mono brand retail concept;
Female Only.
ABOUT THE COMPANY
Al Ghurair is a diversified industrial group based in Dubai with operations spanning more than 50 countries globally. With a rich history of pioneering businesses and technologies, this heritage of innovative success is built upon values of excellence in the products developed and the processes followed. Our Core Areas of Expertise are Foods, Commodities, Construction and Properties. And furthermore, our additional areas of focus include Energy, Printing, Retail and Education.
